    reflection: ["Sandalwood Base (N)", "Benzoin (N)", "Iris Root (N)", "Benzoin Siam (N)", "Orris Concrete (N)", "Benzoin-Thai-Crystal-(N)", "Iris-Florentine-Rhizome-(N)"],
